<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <header class="mb-6 flex items-baseline justify-between">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">🛂 Hermes Audit</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">이 사업장에 기록된 모든 운영 행위의 감사 로그입니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">최근 200건</div>
    </header>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-3 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-3">
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">오늘</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800"><%= @stats[:today] %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-3">
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">7일</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800"><%= @stats[:week] %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-3">
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">전체</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800"><%= @stats[:total] %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-3">
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">운영자</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-700"><%= @stats[:operator] %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-3">
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">시스템</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-600"><%= @stats[:system] %></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-between">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm">감사 이벤트 (Audit Trail)</h2>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-500"><%= @events.size %>건</span>
      </div>
      <% if @events.any? %>
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-slate-100 text-xs uppercase text-slate-600">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left">시각</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left">주체</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left">액션</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left">대상</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left">메타데이터</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% @events.each do |e| %>
              <tr class="border-t border-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-xs text-slate-600 whitespace-nowrap">
                  <%= l(e.occurred_at || e.created_at, format: :short) rescue (e.occurred_at || e.created_at).strftime("%m-%d %H:%M:%S") %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2">
                  <span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium
                    <%= case e.actor_kind
                        when 'operator' then 'bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700'
                        when 'system' then 'bg-slate-200 text-slate-700'
                        when 'sohee' then 'bg-pink-100 text-pink-700'
                        else 'bg-slate-100 text-slate-600'
                        end %>">
                    <%= e.actor_kind.presence || "-" %>
                  </span>
                </td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-slate-700"><%= e.action %></td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-xs text-slate-600">
                  <% if e.resource_type %>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><%= e.resource_type %></span>
                    <span class="text-slate-700">#<%= e.resource_id %></span>
                  <% else %>
                    <span class="text-slate-300">—</span>
                  <% end %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-4 py-2 text-xs text-slate-500 max-w-xs truncate">
                  <%= e.metadata.is_a?(Hash) ? anonymize_person(e.metadata.to_json[0, 80]) : e.metadata.to_s[0, 80] %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      <% else %>
        <p class="px-4 py-12 text-center text-slate-400 text-sm">아직 기록된 감사 이벤트가 없습니다.</p>
      <% end %>
    </section>

    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400">
      ※ 모든 운영 행위는 변경 전·후가 기록되며, 외부 노출은 차단됩니다. 익명화 헬퍼로 처리되었습니다.
    </p>
  </main>
</div>